scp.Name: SCP: Secret Laboratory
scp.Description: Multiplayer Containment Breach with improved graphics. Server runs various plugins to keep repetition down.

sandbox.Name: Sandbox (Garry's Mod)
sandbox.Description: Server from an old community, contains addons from other servers put together in a sandbox environment with dozens of maps.

various.Name: Various Gamemodes (Garry's Mod)
various.Description: This server currently hosts the following gamemodes: Cops and Runners, Flood, Homicide, Jazztronauts, Prop Hunt, Pirate Ship Wars Remix, Pirates Vs Boners, Dropzone, Sledbuild, Stop it Slender, TTT, Trash Compactor, and Zombie Survival.

vanilla.Name: Vanilla (Minecraft)
vanilla.Description: Always runs the most recent release of the game. Multiple maps to choose from.

synergy.Name: Synergy
synergy.Description: Multiplayer Half-Life 2. Also supports Episodes 1 and 2.

modded.Name: OG Modded (Minecraft)
modded.Description: Original modded Minecraft server. Contains around 50 various mods. Players are in survival mode. Runs on version 1.12.2.

unbalanced.Name: Unbalanced (Minecraft)
unbalanced.Description: Modded Minecraft server that contains around 60 OP mods that were rejected from other servers. Players are in survival mode. Runs on version 1.12.2. WARNING: Some PCs may struggle to run this modpack.

unbalanced2.Name: Unbalanced 2 (Minecraft)
unbalanced2.Description: Modded Minecraft server that contains around 60 OP mods that were rejected or never added to other servers. Players are in survival mode. Runs on version 1.12.2. WARNING: Some PCs may struggle to run this modpack.

rlcraft.Name: RLCraft (Minecraft)
rlcraft.Description: Runs the most recent version of the RLCraft modpack. Not recommended for people with low amounts of patience.

protocol.Name: Broke Protocol: Online City RPG
protocol.Description: Cool indie game that sorta mixes Minecraft with CityRP and GTA Online.

earth.Name: Earth (Minecraft)
earth.Description: Modded minecraft server that runs the 1:1 scale Earth mod along with various other mods with the goal of simply building. Players are in creative mode by default but have admin privileges to switch to other modes if needed. Runs on version 1.12.2.

hlurp.Name: Half-Life Universe RP (Garry's Mod)
hlurp.Description: Custom gamemode based on the major events of the official Half-Life games.

cityrp.Name: CityRP (Garry's Mod)
cityrp.Description: Plays like the default DarkRP gamemode but more advanced and takes place in a modern city environment. Rules are similar to those seen on Lawless RP servers.
